title: Alien Ant Farm Live In Tempe 2008
description:
Hi! 8) 

It\&#039;s been a while since I\&#039;ve uploaded something. Today I have something really cool for you. Alien Ant Farm performed live and acoustic in Tempe, AZ on June 19th 2008.

The whole set is available for free as usual. This time I\&#039;ve added few more trackers so other people could download the torrent as well.


Here\&#039;s the track list:

[b]Acoustic Mini-Show[/b]
Glow
Stranded
Tia Lupe
Attitude
Movies

[b]Sound Check before the proper concert[/b]
Band plays few songs, including Weezer\&#039;s song, Sticks & Stones, Goodbye and Glow. Goofing around basically.

[b]Live Show[/b]
Courage
Whisper
1000 Days
Drifting Apart
Movies
Stranded
Attitude
Glow
Sticks and Stones
Goodbye
S.S. Recognize
Smooth Criminal

Well that\&#039;s it, gallery from the show and lots of more available on alienantfans.com

PS
[b]Did you know that this summer Alien Ant Farm is going to record some new tracks?[/b] And right after that (somewhere in September I assume) they\&#039;re going to play few live shows. But not just ordinary shows. Most of you must know what\&#039;s [b]Bluetooth technology[/b] right? If you have a Bluetooth cell phone, iPhone or any other device [b]you can bring it with you to the show and simply turn it on to get FREE AAF videos, songs and of course THE NEW SONGS.[/b]

Goodbye for now! Stay tuned for more shows!
